al]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[2014 Cannes Film Festival|14 \u2013 25 May 2014]]\n| [[Jury Prize (Cannes Film Festival)|Prix du Jury]]\n| {{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=1|<ref name=\"2014Winners\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[C\u00e9sar Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[40th C\u00e9sar Awards|20 February 2015]]\n| [[C\u00e9sar Award for Best Foreign Film|Best Foreign Film]]\n| {{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=1|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allocine.fr/article/fichearticle_gen_carticle=18639388.html|title=C\u00e9sar 2015 : les nominations|accessdate=29 January 2015|work=[[AlloCin\u00e9]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411014248/http://www.allocine.fr/article/fichearticle_gen_carticle=18639388.html|archive-date=11 April 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> \n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[Chicago Film Critics Association]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[Chicago Film Critics Association Awards 2014|15 December 2014]]\n| [[Chicago Film Critics Association Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]]\n!\n| {{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=1|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagofilmcritics.org/awards/130-birdman-leads-2014-cfca-nominations|title=\"Birdman\" Leads 2014 CFCA Nominations|accessdate=14 December 2014|work=CFCA|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127051249/http://www.chicagofilmcritics.org/awards/130-birdman-leads-2014-cfca-nominations|archive-date=27 November 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[David di Donatello Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | 12 June 2015\n| [[David di Donatello for Best Foreign Film|Best Foreign Film]]\n| Xavier Dolan\n| {{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=1|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/birdman-wins-italys-david-di-802144 |title='Birdman' Wins Italy's David Di Donatello Award for Best Foreign Picture |last=Anderson |first=Ariston |date=12 June 2015 |accessdate=17 August 2016 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |archive-url=https://web.arc